  "keyFeatures": [
    "Spec-driven development workflow for AI coding assistants",
    "Slash commands (/opsx:propose, /opsx:apply, /opsx:archive) for 20+ AI tools",
    "Artifact-based change management (proposal, specs, design, tasks)",
    "Delta specs for brownfield development — ADDED/MODIFIED/REMOVED sections",
    "Custom workflow schemas with artifact dependency graphs",
    "CLI for validation, status inspection, and project management",
    "Parallel change support with conflict-free spec merging",
    "Agent-compatible JSON output for programmatic use"
